title: Dakotas Biggest Fan (21roles) 2015
description:
You're not one to be obsessed with celebrities except for one person. The famous and beautiful Dakota Ryan. Your phone's wallpaper? Yep. A photo of her. A true fan of hers. When you least expect it, like a dream, Dakota rings your doorbell asking for your help. This is your chance to spend 24 wonderful hours together with your beloved celebrity in your own house. Can you seduce her? Can she seduce you? More than one surprise awaits you... time to find out what they are!
